data.description: Beautiful single family home in the desirable Kiln Creek community. Home features a fenced backyard with large deck, eat in kitchen with oak cabinets & updated appliances, family room with gas fireplace, vinyl plank flooring throughout the 1st floor, and spacious owner's suite. Community offers pools, tennis courts, pickleball courts, fitness center with personal trainer, clubhouse, playgrounds, walking trails, bird trails, community events, golf course, restaurants, and so much more! Make sure to view the 3D interactive tour to view more of this beautiful home!
